    • Method Summary

      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      <L> java.util.List<java.lang.String> getRegionNames(L location)
      Returns all region names at the given location.
      <L> void prepareSpawningRegion(L location)
      Prepares the given location for spawning a pet inside of it. All worldguard regions get modified to correctly adjust the spawning. Does nothing if already prepared.
      <L> void resetSpawningRegion(L location)
      Resets the cached spawning adjustments which where made by DependencyWorldGuardService.prepareSpawningRegion. If no caches are present it does nothing.
